    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Science or profession concerned with the teeth and associated structures of the mouth, involving the prevention, diagnosis, and treatment of disease, injury, or malformation of the teeth, gums, and jaws.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
